Package: sbyops
Type: Package
Title: Modal-Frequency Near-Zero-Variance Filter
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Joao B. G.", "de Brito", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "JoaoSabby@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Detects columns with low variability by modal frequency using an R
    interface and a Fortran native core. Columns are flagged when the most common
    value reaches a user-defined frequency threshold.
